{"word":"βροντάω","slug":"βροντάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βροντάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:βροντή'><el>βροντή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to thunder</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> of Pericles, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:impersonal'>impers.</a>, <el>βροντᾶι</el> <i>it thunders</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}